Lab -1 SRS (College information System)

The system would be used by the Principal, Teachers, HOD's, Strudents, Non Teaching Staff and accounts section.

Teachers can add new assignments or tests.
Teachers can take attendance.
Teachers can teach in the class and conduct labs.
The students can mark present, Complete their pending tasks and study.
The HOD can conduct the semester.
The HOD can take reports from the teacher as well as report to the Principal.
The non teaching staff can perform their duties.
The accounts section can create fee slips, process Fee payments and carry out payments to the staff.
The accounts section can also send reminders to the students.
The principal can make policies, check for reports and appoint the staff.
